what is secret recovery phrase descripti:
Secret recovery phrase is used to derive multiple private keys. It is a unique wallet phrase that gives you a human readable format of words to backup your wallet for recovery. It is typically a phrase that allows you to access an infinite number of accounts. At its purest form it is a pattern of letters, words or associations that help you remember the information easily. It is used by Ledger, TREZOR, MetaMask, Jaxx and others.

The accounts you can access with this phrase are determined by the specific "derivation path". Wallets dervied from this method is called "Hierarchical Deterministic wallets" or HD wallets. Forbole X allows you to import a wallet using the secret recovery from different derivation paths.

Here is an example of what it should look like:

review cereal bean admit critic oven piece ginger engage dog donor safe amount front swamp recycle west rebel one erosion vicious access salt faint

Remember: We do not save your wallet password and secret recovery phrase in our server, once forgotten, it cannot be recovered and you cannot access to your fund from the corresponding wallets.

about forbole x detail:
Forbole X is the gateway to the crypto universe. Forbole X is built for token holders who would like to manage ALL their crypto assets in a secured and easy way. It is a non-custodial crypto wallet that provides all sorts of transaction activities, including sending, receiving, staking, and on-chain governance participation. It also supports more complex activities through inter-blockchain communications (IBC), such as DeFi, AMM, NFTs, staking derivatives and connection with decentralized exchanges.

Forbole-X comes with some premium accounting and asset management functions. There is a significant demand for integrated crypto asset management tools, as more and more companies and institutional investors are holding cryptos in their portfolios. A multi-asset portfolio management tool with extensive accounting reports will come in handy for investors and portfolio managers.

Forbole X is more than a wallet. We envision it as a comprehensive crypto asset management platform for crypto enthusiasts and professionals.
